Pod-POM-View-HTML-Filter

Pod::POM::View::HTML::Filter is a Pod::POM view used to filter
some specially marked pod blocks.

It was first designed to output syntax-hightlighted Perl on some
static webpages. Look, here: http://articles.mongueurs.net/magazines/

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


